comments: Curry (GSW) places an arm against Hunter's (ATL) side as he moves along his path and the contact is marginal.  Hunter loses control of the ball on his own.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Hunter (ATL) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
DiVincenzo (GSW) establishes himself in Hunter's (ATL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Young (ATL) briefly grabs Curry's (GSW) arm, but the contact does not affect his ability to make the pass.
After Collins (ATL) secures the rebound, incidental body contact occurs with Curry (GSW).
Curry (GSW) is drawn into the air during the shot fake and initiates lower body contact with Murray (ATL) during his upward shooting motion.
Curry (GSW) brings his hands toward Murray (ATL) off ball and marginal contact occurs as Curry releases away to retrieve the pass.
Lamb (GSW) dislodges Collins (ATL) from his position as he secures the rebound.
Young (ATL) reaches in while defending Curry (GSW) and he makes clean contact with the ball to deflect it away.
Poole (GSW) Collins (ATL) mutually engage on the perimeter and marginal contact occurs as the pick is set.
Poole (GSW) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
